targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias(created_time_start,$__interval,0),
  sum(total_tracking_number) AS "total_tracking_number"
FROM event_instance_reporting 
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created_time_start)
  and event_type in  (${event_type})
  and event in  (${event})
  and courierCode in  (${courierCode})
  and executed in  (${executed})
  and enabled in  (${enabled})
   
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
  $__timeGroupAlias(created_time_start,$__interval,0),
  sum(retry_count_0) AS "retry_count_0",
  sum(retry_count_1) AS "retry_count_1",
  sum(retry_count_2) AS "retry_count_2",
  sum(retry_count_3) AS "retry_count_3",

  sum(retry_count_5) AS "retry_count_5"
